Class AggregatedData

java.lang.Object
com.kf7014.smartcitymicroservice.model.AggregatedData
public class AggregatedData extends Object
Represents aggregated consumption data for a specific provider over a defined period.

This model maps to the aggregated_data collection in MongoDB and stores summary statistics such as total and average consumption for each provider within a particular aggregation period.

The aggregation period is typically represented in the format "YYYY-MM-DD".
